OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1773151900
OL,3,CWrexham denied Hollywood ending by VAR
OL,4,Cas Chelsea survive FA Cup scare
OL,6,FChelsea twice came from behind to
OL,7,Favoid an FA Cup shock with a 4-2 extra-
OL,8,Ftime victory at 10-man Wrexham.
OL,10,FWith Hollywood owners Ryan Reynolds
OL,11,Fand Rob Mac in attendance, the
OL,12,Fambitious Welsh outfit were dreaming
OL,13,Fof a famous victory when they took the
OL,14,Flead at a raucous Stok Cae Ras through
OL,15,FSam Smith.
OL,17,FA fortuitous own goal allowed the
OL,18,Fsluggish Londoners to equalise but the
OL,19,FRed Dragons' hopes were rekindled with
OL,20,Fan improvised finish from Callum Doyle
OL,21,F12 minutes from time.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
