OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1773151900
OL,3,CWrexham denied Hollywood ending by VAR
OL,4,Cas Chelsea survive FA Cup scare
OL,6,FYet it was not to be as Josh
OL,7,FAcheampong levelled for a second time
OL,8,Fand Alejandro Garnacho and Joao Pedro
OL,9,Fsecured Chelsea's quarter-final spot
OL,10,Fin extra time after the hosts had
OL,11,FGeorge Dobson sent off.
OL,13,FWrexham felt they deserved more and
OL,14,Fthought they had made it 3-3 before
OL,15,FPedro's late strike through Lewis
OL,16,FBrunt but his effort was ruled
OL,17,Fnarrowly offside by VAR in a pulsating
OL,18,Ffinish.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
