CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1773151900
OL,3,CWrexham denied Hollywood ending by VAR
OL,4,Cas Chelsea survive FA Cup scare
OL,6,FThe memory of how they came close to
OL,7,Fupsetting the reigning club world
OL,8,Fchampions could also sustain them
OL,9,Fthrough their play-off push.
OL,11,FWith Wednesday's trip to Paris St
OL,12,FGermain in mind, Chelsea made nine
OL,13,Fchanges and left the likes of Cole
OL,14,FPalmer, Moises Caicedo and Enzo
OL,15,FFernandez at home.Consequently their
OL,16,Ffirst-half display was disjointed and
OL,17,FWrexham took advantage.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
