OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1773151900
OL,3,CWrexham denied Hollywood ending by VAR
OL,4,Cas Chelsea survive FA Cup scare
OL,6,FTheir direct approach paid off after
OL,7,F18 minutes as Smith latched onto a
OL,8,Flong ball from Doyle and placed a firm
OL,9,Fshot beyond Robert Sanchez from 18
OL,10,Fyards.
OL,12,FSmith could have capitalised on
OL,13,FChelsea's sloppiness further as he was
OL,14,Freleased again by Doyle but slipped
OL,15,Fafter delaying his shot.
OL,17,FChelsea's equaliser came against the
OL,18,Frun of play after 40 minutes and
OL,19,Finvolved a huge slice of luck.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
