OL,3,CWrexham denied Hollywood ending by VAR
OL,4,Cas Chelsea survive FA Cup scare
OL,6,FLiam Delap did well to turn and break
OL,7,Ffrom halfway but Garnacho's shot
OL,8,Flooked ineffective until it was hacked
OL,9,Foff the line by George Thomason and
OL,10,Frebounded into the net off goalkeeper
OL,11,FArthur Okonkwo.
OL,13,FThe second half was an end-to-end
OL,14,Faffair and both sides had numerous
OL,15,Fchances.
OL,17,FWrexham felt they should have had a
OL,18,Fpenalty when a shot from Ollie
OL,19,FRathbone appeared to strike the arm of
OL,20,FMarc Guiu.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
