PN,46607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1773151900
OL,3,CWrexham denied Hollywood ending by VAR
OL,4,Cas Chelsea survive FA Cup scare
OL,6,FThe hosts dramatically reclaimed the
OL,7,Flead with Doyle's brilliant,
OL,8,Finstinctive finish.
OL,10,FJosh Windass fired a shot into a
OL,11,Fcrowded area after Chelsea failed to
OL,12,Fclear a corner and Doyle reacted
OL,13,Fbrilliantly to flick past Sanchez.
OL,15,FBut they were in front for just four
OL,16,Fminutes as Acheampong slammed into the
OL,17,Froof of the net after Dobson lost
OL,18,Fpossession.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/9
