OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1773151900
OL,3,CWrexham denied Hollywood ending by VAR
OL,4,Cas Chelsea survive FA Cup scare
OL,6,FNeto fired against the crossbar as
OL,7,FChelsea sought a late winner and
OL,8,FDobson's night got worse as he was
OL,9,Fsent off following a VAR review for a
OL,10,Fhigh challenge on Garnacho.
OL,12,FMax Cleworth might have snatched
OL,13,Fvictory for the 10 men in stoppage
OL,14,Ftime but his powerful strike was too
OL,15,Fclose to Sanchez and Chelsea made
OL,16,Ftheir advantage tell in the first
OL,17,Fperiod of extra time.
OL,19,FGarnacho volleyed in from close range
OL,20,Ffrom a Dario Essugo cross.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/9
