OL,3,CWrexham denied Hollywood ending by VAR
OL,4,Cas Chelsea survive FA Cup scare
OL,6,FWrexham thought they had made it 3-3
OL,7,Fwhen Brunt turned in from Kieffer
OL,8,FMoore's glancing header but he was
OL,9,Fjust offside.
OL,11,FPhil Parkinson's men kept on pushing
OL,12,Fbut Pedro had the final say.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/9
